        "content": "## Self-hosted n8n Community Edition\n\n**No Settings → Variables** on the free plan. Edit the **Config: Edit These Values** Set node (yellow fields) in each workflow instead.\n\nOptional: you can also set OS/Docker env vars on the n8n container — not required if you use the Config node.\n\n**Trigger:** questionnaire.submitted\n\nEdit Config: `crm_base_url` for feedback links.",
